short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Check how much it cost to travel

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds fuel cost to Google Maps when you plan a journey.
Ever thought "How much will this journey cost me exactly"? Install this free extension and find out!

Adds fuel cost to Google Maps when you plan a journey.

This Extension is Supported for Different Currencies, Different Fuel Units (litre, gallon, kWh), One-Way/Two-Way Trip.

Please send feedback to the Linkedin Profile present inside the extension.

This is alpha software, please report bugs instead of leaving bad reviews, thanks!

This Extension is not affiliated with or endorsed or sponsored by Google Maps.
